      "y": 430,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## UNIT-1: removeBuildArtifacts\n\n**Score:** Composite 2\n**Goal:** Remove build directory artifacts\n**Input \u2192 Output:** build directory config \u2192 removal result\n**Deps:** none"
