      "y": 640,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## UNIT-12A: parseTypeScriptExports\n\n**Score:** Composite 2\n**Goal:** Parse TypeScript export statements\n**Signature:** AnalysisConfig \u2192 ExportParseResult\n**Test:** bun test src/analysis/unused-exports.test.ts\n**Deps:** none"
