      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 850,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## UNIT-17A: buildFileDependencyGraph\n\n**Score:** Composite 2\n**Goal:** Build file dependency graph\n**Signature:** AnalysisConfig \u2192 DependencyGraphResult\n**Test:** bun test src/analysis/unreferenced-files.test.ts\n**Deps:** none"
