      "x": -200,
      "y": 1270,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## UNIT-52A: analyzeCurrentStructure\n\n**Score:** Composite 2\n**Goal:** Analyze current project structure\n**Signature:** ReadmeConfig \u2192 StructureAnalysisResult\n**Test:** bun test src/documentation/readme-updater.test.ts\n**Deps:** none"
