      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 830,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## UNIT-12B: trackExportUsage\n\n**Score:** Composite 2\n**Goal:** Track export usage across codebase\n**Signature:** ExportParseResult & AnalysisConfig \u2192 UsageTrackingResult\n**Test:** bun test src/analysis/unused-exports.test.ts\n**Deps:** UNIT-12A"
