    {
      "id": "781d1af62a2ae8a4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 1040,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## UNIT-17B: identifyGraphOrphans\n\n**Score:** Composite 2\n**Goal:** Identify orphaned files in dependency graph\n**Signature:** DependencyGraphResult \u2192 UnreferencedFilesReport\n**Test:** bun test src/analysis/unreferenced-files.test.ts\n**Deps:** UNIT-17A"
    },
    {
      "id": "00f5ef4add4ff7b5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -200,
      "y": 1250,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "## UNIT-21B: validateLayerRules\n\n**Score:** Composite 2\n**Goal:** Validate architectural layer rules\n**Signature:** DirectoryScanResult \u2192 LayerValidationReport\n**Test:** bun test src/validation/layer-structure.test.ts\n**Deps:** UNIT-21A"
